{"head":{"description":"selector-root-no-composition Deprecated: instead use the community stylelint-suitcss plugin pack Disallow the composition of :root in…","title":"selector-root-no-composition"},"body":"<h1 id=\"selector-root-no-composition\"><a href=\"#selector-root-no-composition\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>selector-root-no-composition</h1>\n<p><strong><em>Deprecated: instead use the community <a href=\"https://github.com/suitcss/stylelint-suitcss\"><code>stylelint-suitcss</code></a> plugin pack</em></strong></p>\n<p>Disallow the composition of <code>:root</code> in selectors.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">    <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span>, <span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:root</span> {}\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/** ↑  ↑\n * This type of composite selector */</span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Options</h2>\n<h3 id=\"true\"><a href=\"#true\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>true</code></h3>\n<p>The following patterns are considered warnings:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span>, <span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:root</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:root</span> + <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">html</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:root</span> {}</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered warnings:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:root</span> {}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/selector-root-no-composition.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/selector-root-no-composition/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-root-no-composition/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-root-no-composition/index.html.57e0bb7f27c435b965df045cb5f3b740.json"}